@{b}@{u}Note@{uu}@{ub} that the combination of Surface/BlocksPerTrack and HighCyl may differ from controller to controller since all media are projected to an endless byte stream. All combinations that result in ~196520 blocks are correct. In the above example a layout of 2 surfaces by 34 BlocksPerTrack by 2890 Tracks is also satisfying.

